      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay thanks. i dont really want to call the doctor in the middle of the day if i don't have to, it's such a hassle. if i just drink a ton of water and keep taking the pills, it'll probably level out soon right? like the nausea will go away once my body gets used to it?",
